---

<Layout>
	<main class="grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-12 min-h-screen">
		<header class="flex flex-col justify-end col-span-5 row-span-5 bg-stone-900">
			<h1 class="text-8xl leading-[1.1] p-8 text-right tracking-loose"><span class="text-stone-700">An</span> Unusual<br />Undertaking</h1>
		</header>
		<div class="flex flex-col justify-start col-span-7 row-span-7 row-start-5 col-start-6 bg-stone-900">
			<h2 class="text-8xl leading-[1.1] p-8 tracking-loose">A studio specializing in art, game dev, and building software products.</h2>
		</div>
	</main>
	<section class="grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-12 min-h-screen -mt-[165px]">
		<header class="flex flex-col justify-end col-span-4 col-start-2 row-span-2 row-start-2 bg-stone-900">
			<h3 class="text-4xl leading-[1.1] p-8 text-right tracking-loose"><span class="text-stone-700">A</span> Solo Undertaking</h3>
		</header>
		<div class="flex flex-col justify-start col-span-7 row-span-6 row-start-2 col-start-6 bg-stone-900">
			<p class="text-4xl leading-[1.1] p-8 pb-4 tracking-loose">Iâ€™m Tim, artist/game dev/engineer and the sole founder and member of Unusual Undertaking.</p>
			<p class="text-4xl leading-[1.1] p-8 pt-4 pb-4 tracking-loose">I operate on a strong belief that approaching projects with a multi-disciplinary and generalist perspective yields the most interesting results.</p>
			<p class="text-4xl leading-[1.1] p-8 pt-4 tracking-loose">When you skillfully combine art and engineering, you end up making things people love.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-12 min-h-screen -mt-[300px]">
		<div class="flex flex-col justify-start col-span-7 row-span-6 bg-stone-900">
			<p class="text-4xl leading-[1.1] p-8 pb-4 tracking-loose">Currently accepting work involving building:<br /><br /><span class="text-green-400">Fullstack web apps</span> / creative coding projects / unique websites / game prototypes / browser-based games</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
